features: 【Cozy Material】: The queen comforter set is made of premium quality brushed microfiber material with soft polyester inner fill, which is ultra soft and cozy. This ruffled comforter set is lighter than you think and touches smooth and comfortable, durable and lightweight to use. Greatly improve your sleep quality, ensuring you wake up feeling refreshed.

【Vintage Ruffled Design】: Our Grayish Purple comforter set adopt vintage style and featuring small tufted ruffled, sensory and texture are extremely comfortable, which perfectly blends graceful and abstract art, add an extra layer of art and classic style to match your room décor and brighten your rooms. Perfect as a great gift idea for men and women at special festivals, such as housewarming, Christmas, Thanksgiving and birthday, etc.

【YEAR ROUND】: The bed queen size comforter set’s weight is ideal for year-round use. The ruffled comforter set keeps you warm in the winter and fits to use in the summer. Our bedding comforters & sets can be used directly without duvet cover. Reduce your time on changing the bed. As well as being a alternative comforter with your favorite duvet cover.

【Simple and Classic】: This ruffled comforter set is designed with ruffles stitched, add a hint of art to your furniture and home decor. And solid color will never outmoded, suitable for any color scheme and room style. Choosing our ruffle comforter, you will get 1 Grayish Purple comforter set (90x90 inches)and 2 pillowcases(20x26 inches). The pillowcases adopt the same ruffles stitched design.

【Easy Care】: The Grayish Purple comforter is packed in a vacuum bag, when you receive our comforters queen size set purple, just shake and pat it gently until it becomes fluffy. To clean the queen comforter, machine wash separately on cold water with similar colors. On gentle cycle, tumble dry on low heat, do not bleach to keep the color vibrant.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect and Affordable!
reviews.reviewText: It’s a little wrinkled after washing but it’s thick, yet cool and light! It’s super soft and looks great!! Definitely great quality for the price I highly recommend!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars good quality for price
reviews.reviewText: when it first arrived, i was confused because of the small box but turns out it had just been vacuum sealed. it fluffed up really nicely after a few minutes being outside of the box. it wrinkled but it’s expected since it was vacuum sealed. i have no complaints on the comfort, it’s really soft and the material is nice. my only complaint is that when i washed it, some of the stuffing got displaced so some parts of it are chunkier then the rest now, but i’m not going to change the reviews rating just because it was probably a mistake on my end. make sure to put the drier on low, that was probably my mistake. looks good. Peachier, salmon pink rather than a blush pink. cute color. picture does not do it justice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: i love this bedding set so much. i’m super picky with my bedding and tend to buy a lot of it because i have a obsession with changing my room and for the price this is my favorite i’ve bought so far, the ruffles on the sides are so cute and it’s very soft and fluffy. i got red silk sheets to go with it and it’s soooo cute together i definitely reccomend if your thinking about buying it :’)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This comforter is exactly what I was looking for. Light weight, but still warm. It’s also so soft and comfortable. I would have liked for the width to be a little longer, but other than that, it’s perfect!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I won’t lie I was extremely skeptical to order a comforter online. I ordered this and it came in a small box and I was livid. I was thinking this must just be sheets. BUT the comforter is vacuum sealed in the box. Once you cut the plastic it is a huge comforter. Super cute! Super soft! Love this

It's super soft and fluffy, exceeded my expectations. It comes quite wrinkled but I tossed it in the dryer and most of it went away. Something to note: there's only ruffles on 3/4 of the sides. So one of the short ends is ruffle free. Something to keep in mind if you want ruffles both at the end of the bed and also where you fold over the top of the comforter.
I love this comforter! It fits my aesthetic perfectly and it’s good quality!! I love it so much!

reviews.reviewTitle: So soft. Keeps you warm but not too hot!!!
reviews.reviewText: It’a so cute! Colour is perfect, super soft. I love that it only has ruffles on 3/4 of the sides as I don’t like things like that on my face while I sleep. Love it!
